metadata.name: OKAY! Doodle Girls #1
metadata.description: Has Daddy been cranky lately? Seems like he is having less and less time to play? He has probably been arguing with mom too. Things seem too tense and serious around the house. Things are DOWN BAD. But it's going to be OKAY! The Okay Doodle Girls are up to something. They have a plan, and they can move mountains as a team. With hard work and dedication they can do anything together! They know exactly what they need to do to make this all OKAY.
